Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.35,0:42:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你把這些都算在我頭上？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You attribute all that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.82,0:42:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是我的猜測{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I had to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.62,0:42:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有位智者曾告訴我  推測對政治來說是很糟的方式{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A smart man once said to me that  speculation is a poor form of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.12,0:42:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}瑞蒙，何不說你知道的事情？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why don't you stick  to what you know, Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.29,0:42:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道只要你下定決心  就能發揮高度效率{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What I know is you are extremely effective  at what you set your mind to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.87,0:42:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這對我非常有價值{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That is valuable to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.03,0:42:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我已經告訴葛瑞  這對他會很有幫助{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I've already told Garrett  that it could be valuable to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.17,0:42:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在他的團隊裏  能有人一腳在行政部門{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Somebody at his side  with one foot in the Executive Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.54,0:42:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一腳在立法部門{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and one in the Legislative.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.31,0:42:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他對這想法持開放的態度{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He is very open to the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.42,0:42:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}換我猜了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My turn to speculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.55,0:42:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的推薦是有價錢的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your recommendation comes at a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.93,0:43:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒錯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我有你需要的東西  你有我需要的東西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I have something that you want,  you have something that I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.97,0:43:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我說了什麼好笑的話嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Have I said something amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.71,0:43:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我談判時大多是坐在你那邊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've just sat too many times  on your side of the table
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.14,0:43:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在發現自己坐在另一邊  覺得很諷刺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}not to enjoy the irony of finding myself  on this side of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.41,0:43:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}想聽聽我要的是什麼嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Would you like to hear what I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.62,0:43:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會讓自己被陌生人束縛{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't shackle myself to people I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.72,0:43:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只想要一個人情{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What I want is one favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.06,0:43:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只有一個{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}One and only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.36,0:43:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Which is?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.49,0:43:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在我冒險說出細節之前  我需要你先答應{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need to be certain you'll grant it before  I'll take the risk of being more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.40,0:43:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 一張空白支票  - 差不多{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-A blank check.  -Of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你絕對不會開空白支票給別人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You would never grant anyone a blank check.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.47,0:43:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.54,0:43:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我現在不是坐在那一邊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I'm not sitting on that side of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.01,0:43:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在我家鄉  我們仍相信握手的誠信{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We still believe in handshakes  where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.28,0:43:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在華府還流行嗎？  你要打給誰？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do they still mean anything in Washington?  Who are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.82,0:44:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 叫車送我去機場  - 法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Car service to get me to the airport.  -Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.19,0:44:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我會告訴總統  我需要仔細考慮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I will tell the President  that I want until Friday
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.02,0:44:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}週五再給他我的建議{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}to think things over before  I make my recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.46,0:44:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你改變主意就通知我  讓我替你安排車子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let me know ifyou change your mind.  And let me arrange the car for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.13,0:44:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你好，我想叫車{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hi, I'd like to arrange a car, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.63,0:44:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}女廁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.27,0:44:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你還好嗎？  - 比昨天好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-How are you feeling?  -Better than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.77,0:44:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過如果又開始想吐  可能會早退{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I might take off early  if the nausea comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.01,0:44:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我覺得很巧，你打發走  善可工業隔天就沒來上班{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I find it interesting that you stay home the  day after you blow off the SanCorp people.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.78,0:44:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不是不舒服，吉莉安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You weren't feeling sick, Gillian.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.45,0:44:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你指控我利用懷孕做藉口  這樣非常過分{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I find it extremely offensive that you'd  accuse me of hiding behind my pregnancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.29,0:44:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你知道我要什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You knew what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.16,0:44:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}波札納計劃是我的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The Botswana project is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.73,0:44:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在我的保護傘下  用我募來的資金{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Under my umbrella. Using money I raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.63,0:44:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你答應讓我全權處理{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You promised me autonomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.07,0:44:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}麻煩迴避一下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Excuse us for a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.81,0:44:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我答應讓你變強大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I promised to empower you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.48,0:45:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這跟你不徵求我的意見  擅自行動是不一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's not the same thing as you doing  as you choose without consulting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.51,0:45:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會允許  我花了三年時間的計劃…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm not going to allow a project  I've put almost three years of my life into...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.52,0:45:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果沒有善可工業  你的計劃根本不會開始{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your project wouldn't be happening  if it weren't for SanCorp.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.25,0:45:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒要他們幫忙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't ask for their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.39,0:45:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那你簽協議之前  先問問我的意見如何？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How about consulting me  before you struck a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.99,0:45:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有件事你要搞清楚  這個組織是屬於我的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let's get something very clear,  I run the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.43,0:45:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你只是在這裏工作而已{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You work for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.33,0:45:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們的協議是一起聯手  克萊兒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Our agreement is an affiliation, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.00,0:45:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 世安不是你的附屬品  - 它是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-WorldWell isn't your vassal.  -Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.37,0:45:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果要說得這麼白  它完全是我的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Entirely. If we're going to be blunt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.01,0:45:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這不是你六個月前的提議{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's not what you proposed  six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.57,0:45:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的合約上是這麼寫的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's what you signed up for  when you signed the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.61,0:45:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們有很好的信任關係  瞭解…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There was a good faith understanding that...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.94,0:45:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你違抗我  這種信任關係被破壞了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you've dissolved that  good faith by disobeying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.22,0:45:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}違抗你？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Disobeying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.78,0:45:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.59,0:45:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我威脅到你了吧？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I threaten you, don't l?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.09,0:45:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你對我完全不構成威脅{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nothing about you threatens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.76,0:45:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但你也許該休假一陣子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But maybe you should  take a leave of absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.23,0:45:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要開除我嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you firing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.33,0:45:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}隨你怎麼想  但你現在該離開了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's up to you.  But right now, you should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.61,0:46:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你有把她錄下來嗎？  - 沒有，她不會和我談{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Did you get her on record?  -No. She wouldn't talk to me otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.08,0:46:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們需要確切的證據  來證明安德沃是幕後主謀{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, we need hard proof  that Underwood was behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.08,0:46:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這整件事讓我非常緊張{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This whole thing  is making me really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.58,0:46:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}怕你會曝光？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That you'll be exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.75,0:46:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.19,0:46:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是法蘭斯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.89,0:46:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果內幕這麼複雜  他又早就在監視你…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If this really goes as deep as we think,  and he's already watching you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.09,0:46:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你覺得他很危險？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You think he's dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.53,0:46:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道他很危險{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.13,0:46:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以我們才必須繼續{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Then that's why we have to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.27,0:46:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他會把人摧毀，珍妮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He crushes people, Janine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.54,0:46:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你好，卡倫  - 你好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Hey, Callum.  -Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.21,0:46:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}聽著，如果你不害怕  就不會做這份工作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look, if you weren't afraid,  you wouldn't be doing your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.48,0:46:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我寫過真正有價值的報導  都讓我嚇得半死{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The only articles that I have ever written  that truly mattered scared the shit out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.26,0:46:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們需要知道  關於魯索的所有事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We need to know about anything  that might've happened with Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.93,0:46:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}安德沃能用來控制他的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Something Underwood  could have held over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.86,0:46:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們得回去  找克裏絲汀娜葛蘭格{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have to go back to Christina Gallagher,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.13,0:47:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 看她能不能提供什麼線索  - 我不能去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-see if she'll give us something.  -lt can't be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.83,0:47:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 如果我再回去…  - 我去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- If I go back for a second time...  -I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.37,0:47:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你真的不知道  總統和塔斯克的關係密切？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You honestly had no idea that  the President and Tusk were close?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.14,0:47:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在競選過程中和當選後{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He never showed up once  on any call sheet, phone log
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.58,0:47:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他從未出現在電話簿  電話紀錄或行事歷上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}or schedule during the campaign  or since we've been in office.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.65,0:47:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很想相信你，琳達  但這有點困難{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'd love to believe you, Linda,  but I'm finding it very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.45,0:47:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我瞞著你有什麼好處？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What would I gain  by keeping you in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.45,0:47:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我和你一樣震驚，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I am as shocked as you are, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.92,0:47:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 別表現出你知道的樣子  - 當然不會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Well, don't let on that you know.  -Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.29,0:47:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統怎麼說？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What's the President saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.99,0:47:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他想約你週二匯報  有關塔斯克的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He wants to meet with you Tuesday  to get your report on Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.23,0:47:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}真可笑{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's a farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.39,0:47:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要不要我找理由延期？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Should I come up with a reason  to delay the meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.73,0:47:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不，也許能瞭解內情，幾點？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, maybe we'll learn something. What time?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.80,0:47:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 下午2點  - 我會到的，謝謝，琳達{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-2:00 p.m.  -All right, I'll be there. Thank you, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.73,0:47:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們還有一周{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.34,0:47:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 達到什麼目的？  - 找到塔斯克的弱點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-To accomplish what exactly?  -To force Tusk's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.34,0:47:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他想要我欠他人情？不可能  我們得讓他爬著來求我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He wants me beholden to him? No.  We have to make him to come crawling to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.08,0:47:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他的弱點是什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What's his weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.68,0:47:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他的資產{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}His fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.05,0:47:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 那不是他的優點嗎？  - 如果開始減少就不是了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Wouldn't you say that's his strength?  -Not if it's slipping away.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.25,0:47:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要怎麼讓四百億  在一天內消失？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How do you make $40 billion  disappear overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.09,0:48:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不行，但也許我們能製造  處於險境的假象{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can't, but maybe we can create  the illusion that it's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.09,0:48:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你給我他的那份資產簡報{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The brief you gave me on his assets,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.96,0:48:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}核能產業佔了多少？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}how much of his total net worth  is in nuclear power?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.07,0:48:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}大概三分之一{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}About a third.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.33,0:48:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}國內有16座反應爐  國外有37座{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sixteen reactors here in the States,  37 worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.70,0:48:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這就是我們的目標  從他的核能收益下手{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, that's what we hit him with.  We go after his nuclear interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.47,0:48:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就算如此，他的其他投資  還有250億…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Even so, he's got $25 billion  in other investments...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.34,0:48:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}道格，他是白手起家的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Doug, this is a man who built  his fortune from nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.51,0:48:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}錢對他來說不算什麼  重要的是背後代表的意義{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The money doesn't mean anything to him.  It's what it represents.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.78,0:48:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}什麼意義？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Which is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.85,0:48:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他畢生的努力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}His life's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.08,0:48:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}打給瑞米丹頓  盡快安排個會議{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Get Remy Danton on the phone.  Set up a meeting as quickly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.66,0:48:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}塔斯克瞭解  權力和金錢之間的差別{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tusk understands the difference  between power and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.39,0:48:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以他是個危險人物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's precisely what makes him dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.43,0:48:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他衡量財富的標準  不是私人飛機，而是收買靈魂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He doesn't measure his wealth  in private jets, but purchased souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.57,0:48:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我付出這麼多努力  眼看一伸手就能得到獎賞了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've worked too hard  to get within arm's reach of the prize
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.87,0:48:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我絕不會在得到之前  讓我的手砍掉的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}only to have my hand cut off  just before I seize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.94,0:48:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是喬伊邦斯  來見克裏絲汀娜葛蘭格{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Zoe Barnes, here to see Christina Gallagher.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.34,0:48:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉，沒有你的預約{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry, I don't see an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.81,0:48:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一定是搞錯了，我約了11點半{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There must be a mistake. I have an 1 1:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.98,0:48:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}請稍等{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.85,0:49:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我叫喬伊邦斯，在《頭條報導》工作  你和我同事珍妮史柯斯基聊過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My name is Zoe Barnes, I work at Slugline.  You spoke to my colleague, Janine Skorsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.49,0:49:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 小姐  - 我們沒事，謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Miss.  -We're fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.26,0:49:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不能就這樣進來…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You can't just come in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.86,0:49:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得有些事是你不知道的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There are things you don't know about Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.83,0:49:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我寫了羅伊卡普奈的報導…  - 請馬上離開{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I wrote the article about Roy Kapeniak...  -Please leave. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.57,0:49:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是彼得說服他來找我的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It was Peter who convinced him  to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.27,0:49:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}什麼？我不懂…他為什麼…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What? I don't understand... Why would he...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.87,0:49:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有人對他施壓{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Somebody pressured him to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.34,0:49:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他是1月24日晚上  去見卡普奈的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The night of January 24.  That's when he went to speak to Kapeniak.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.38,0:49:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你記得就職典禮前後  有什麼不對勁的事嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you remember anything strange  around the time of the inauguration?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.18,0:49:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他有什麼可能的把柄嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Anything that could have been  held over him?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.79,0:49:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不記得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.15,0:49:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果他捲入某些事  導致他自殺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If he was mixed up in things that  in any way contributed to his suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.76,0:49:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不會想知道嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}wouldn't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.89,0:49:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不想帶給你更多痛苦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm not trying to cause you any more pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.60,0:49:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只想知道真相{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I just want the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.83,0:49:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你比任何人更有權利知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you deserve that more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 哪一天？  - 1月24日{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-What was the date?  -The 24th of January.

